column2: SELECT top # bestObjId, z, ra, dec, plate, mjd, fiberId, run2d,   &&& + cast(run2d as varchar(#)) + &&& + cast(plate as varchar(#)) + &&& + cast(plate as varchar(#)) + &&& + cast(mjd as varchar(#)) + &&& + cast(fiberid as char(#)) + &&& as url FROM specObjAll WHERE survey = &&& AND class = &&& and zWarning = # AND bestObjId > #  AND (z > # AND z < #)  AND (htmid*# & #) < (# * #)
